sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant Web as Web App
    participant API as Supabase RPC / API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Student->>Web: Open clearance source page
    Web->>API: Load requirements + submissions + item status
    API->>DB: Query relevant records
    DB-->>API: Return current data
    API-->>Web: Render requirements

    Student->>Web: Upload file / confirm requirement
    Web->>API: Sync requirement submissions
    API->>DB: Validate ownership and save state
    DB-->>API: Saved rows
    API-->>Web: Updated status

    Student->>Web: Submit for review
    Web->>API: submit_clearance_item_if_complete()
    API->>DB: Check all applicable required requirements
    alt Complete
        DB-->>API: Validation passed
        API->>DB: Update item to submitted + write history
        API-->>Web: Submission successful
    else Incomplete
        DB-->>API: Validation failed
        API-->>Web: Return blocking error
    end
